{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act27side", "eventName": "火山旅夢", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SL-8", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "愛之歌", "storyInfo": "火山數據異常，面對艾雅法拉的堅持，凱勒終於不再逃避過去，在瑙曼夫婦去世後第一次登上火山進行數據探查。晚會被迫結束，眾人開始撤離。卡恩終於找到當年的證據，追上凱勒質問瑙曼夫婦去世的真相。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_beach_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.8, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$storyendjp_intro", "key": "$storyendjp_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾......真是個好聽的名字，我可以直接叫你阿黛爾嗎？", "name": "瑪格娜"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有聽說過嗎，每個第一次爬上火山的人都會做的一件事。", "name": "瑪格娜"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "拍照嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是在岩漿上烤羽獸蛋。", "name": "瑪格娜"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我以我爬過二十七座火山的經歷向你保證，在烤羽獸蛋方面，岩漿和源石火爐沒有任何區別。", "name": "瑪格娜"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之都會被你烤焦就是了。", "name": "卡提亞"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿！明明你每次都吃得很香！", "name": "瑪格娜"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "原來，火山是這個樣子......和書上看起來完全不一樣。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用擔心，阿黛爾。你可以跟在我的後面。我踩過的地面總是結實的。", "name": "卡提亞"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊張的話，要不要拉住我的手？", "name": "瑪格娜"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我......還好......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾，你之前不是問我們為什麼熱愛火山？", "name": "瑪格娜"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我向你保證，只要你親眼見過一次火山爆發，就永遠無法忘記那種感受。", "name": "瑪格娜"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我喜歡靜靜地坐在火山上思考。大地和我們自身都充滿謎團，可能窮盡我們一生都無法解答其萬一，但我非常享受這種解謎的過程。", "name": "瑪格娜"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人類發明了移動城市，卻至今未能完全弄清天災形成的原因，人類利用源石創造了許多工具，卻對這種石頭於我們本身的反噬束手無策。", "name": "卡提亞"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人類應該在面對這些自然的偉力時認清自己的渺小，這樣他們就不會將太多精力投入到無意義的自相殘殺上。", "name": "卡提亞"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿黛爾，不用太在意卡提亞的悲觀論調，畢竟這片大地上不是每個地方都像汐斯塔一樣單純。", "name": "瑪格娜"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為一個捲在貴族矛盾間的學者，卡提亞有些抱怨也是正常的。不過在這些問題上我一直和他有不同的看法。", "name": "瑪格娜"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人當然是渺小的，但也正因為渺小，可以讓我們在這片大地上有容身之處。", "name": "瑪格娜"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你說的對，瑪格娜。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "生命是那樣地渺小，而人偏要以如此渺小的生命向無邊際的大地索要答案，那麼被大地吞沒也是一個可被預見、被接受的命運。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我本該做好準備......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "可是在你們離開以後，我自己要怎麼面對那樣的深淵？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g8_siestavolcanomuseum_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱勒教授，這是一號監測站訊號丟失前的兩個小時裡傳送回來的數據。", "name": "工作人員"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們從來沒有見過這樣的異常，只能請您來判斷......", "name": "工作人員"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_999_1#10$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_999_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地表氣體濃度沒有變化，為什麼溫度突然提升了這麼多？", "name": "凱勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_999_1#10$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果這個數值是真的，那說明汐斯塔火山裡積蓄的能量突然增加了十倍......不，這怎麼想都是不可能的事。", "name": "凱勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_999_1#10$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_999_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......當作異常數據忽視就好。", "name": "凱勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告知市政廳火山活動更加活躍，讓市民們做好準備，我們能做的也沒有別的了。", "name": "凱勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱勒老師，這可能不是普通的數據異常。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還記得，在爸爸媽媽的研究筆記裡，也提到過幾次類似的狀況......火山周圍的溫度異常地高，與其他數值不配對。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然始終找不到原因，但很難用巧合解釋。", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱勒老師，我們不需要去現場確認一下嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_999_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一號監測站就在火山山腰上，現在正是最危險的時候。", "name": "凱勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出現這種數據只可能是儀器出了故障，沒有必要再冒險去現場查驗了。最後的觀測結果的數據可以根據其他觀測站的數據再做校正。", "name": "凱勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_999_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱勒老師，我不明白......", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您一直在說，這次觀測很重要，是許多學者都在等待的機會。這座城市還有幾十萬人的生活可能會受到影響，難道不應該盡可能嚴謹嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果現在逃避......不就等於承認他們的犧牲是毫無意義的？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女孩聲音不大，身體微微顫抖。好像只是這樣認真地表達自己的心思，就要耗費她不少力氣。"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱勒有些恍然。"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_999_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是......", "name": "凱勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_999_1#5$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_999_1#5$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那樣的犧牲怎麼能說是有意義的？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱勒老師，我好像不能說服您......", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您不願意去的話，那我可以自己去嗎......", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_999_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別開玩笑了，現在火山上狀況不明，怎麼可能讓你自己去那麼危險的地方——", "name": "凱勒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_999_1#6$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱勒老師......可以把媽媽的那件防護服，還給我嗎？", "name": "阿黛爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g6_siestaunbuiltland_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們除了吃東西，還有什麼別的事情可以做？再這麼吃下去我肚子就要撐爆了......", "name": "路人A"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再聽兩首吉他曲？", "name": "路人B"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......感覺應該會有點更有意思的事情才對的......", "name": "路人A"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在哪有黑曜石音樂節好玩呀？那麼多人，那麼多遊客，看不到尾的街道和店鋪，永遠也停不下來的音樂聲。那個時候多好！", "name": "路人B"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在這個晚會，倒是讓我想起了第一次黑曜石音樂節的樣子。", "name": "冰品店店主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一次黑曜石音樂節？那都是多少年前的事了？", "name": "路人B"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在都沒幾個人記得了，第一次黑曜石音樂節其實就是在礦坑裡，是一群礦上的工人辦的。", "name": "冰品店店主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，沒幾個人，也沒有一個像樣的樂手，就那樣隨手彈著曲子，唱著自己編的歌，就這麼辦了起來......", "name": "冰品店店主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個時候哪能想到後來能辦得那麼大，吸引了多少人來。", "name": "冰品店店主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們這個晚會還會有下次嗎？", "name": "路人A"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈，這誰都沒法給個定論啊！", "name": "冰品店店主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可要是搬去市中心那邊，你們這些店是不是都不會再開了？", "name": "路人B"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該是吧，可能也該換個活法了。誰的生活又是一成不變的呢。", "name": "樂器店男老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，以後我們也會在空了的時候來這裡，擺一下攤，彈幾首歌，有人來的話就請他吃兩串，沒人的話就我們自己看看海，看看對面。", "name": "樂器店男老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還從之前的沙灘上帶了一罐沙子來這裡呢！", "name": "樂器店男老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1001_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......要是火山爆發的話，之前的地方就全都是火山灰了吧。", "name": "樂器店女老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1001_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們走過的路，我們轉過的小店，我們踩過的沙灘，都會被蓋在火山灰下面吧。", "name": "樂器店女老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1001_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你也會記得今天我們在這裡辦的晚會，是不是？", "name": "樂器店男老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1001_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......當然，這也是新的記憶。", "name": "樂器店女老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1001_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wdnguitarpizz", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.4, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆撥動手中的吉他，遠處傳來其他人嬉鬧的聲音。"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你們不跳舞嗎？", "name": "冰品店店主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個時候該跳舞了，年輕人們！像現在這樣吃吃喝喝聊聊天，可算不上晚會啊！", "name": "冰品店店主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，讓我也換首曲子彈！", "name": "樂器店男老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那邊那位女士，一起嗎？", "name": "樂器店男老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "伯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_993_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wdnguitarstrum", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伯德撥動琴弦，悠揚的小調環繞著這片地塊。人們躺倒在草地上，看著夜空、螢火和繁星點點。"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滋滋啦啦，一陣不和諧的電流聲響起。"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據觀測到的火山反應，汐斯塔火山很可能會在數小時之內爆發。", "name": "廣播聲"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "移動城市已經遠離火山爆發的影響範圍，請大家不用驚慌。", "name": "廣播聲"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火山爆發的震動可能會引發海嘯，請所有市民立即離開海邊，請所有市民立即離開海邊。", "name": "廣播聲"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就要爆發了？今天？現在？真是挑了個不好的時候。", "name": "路人A"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許也是個好時候。", "name": "路人B"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼叫快離開海邊？這裡會被淹嗎？那這些東西還要不要了？留在這裡會被沖走的吧？", "name": "路人A"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別拿了，先離開要緊吧！", "name": "路人B"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆停下彈琴的手，看向自己的伴侶。燒烤的油煙仍未消散，她臉上有著還未褪去的快樂的紅暈。"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她遺憾地放下手中的燒烤鐵籤。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1001_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，可能在我們離開之後，海浪會吞掉我們今天的腳印......包括我的燒烤架，你的吉他。", "name": "樂器店女老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1001_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來是火山和大海來幫我們和過去的東西告別了。", "name": "樂器店男老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們該往上走了，上面不會被海水淹沒，我們還會有新的生活。", "name": "樂器店男老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1001_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在市中心那裡嗎？我總擔心那裡太狹窄，放不下你所有的樂器，也放不下我的燒烤架。", "name": "樂器店女老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1001_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是能放得下你和我。", "name": "樂器店男老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老闆看著自己伴侶的眼睛，他的眼睛閃閃發亮。"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她突然笑了起來。"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1001_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......也對！那其實就夠了！", "name": "樂器店女老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1001_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對啊，親愛的，那其實就夠了。", "name": "樂器店男老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧！快把湯姆爺爺拉上，看他行動那麼緩慢，別哭著捨不得自己的寶貝冰淇淋。", "name": "樂器店男老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1001_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂——湯姆爺爺——！快走啦！要不然海浪過來，你就要和你的冰淇淋漂流去了！", "name": "樂器店女老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1001_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呦......哎呦......", "name": "冰品店店主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個幫我搬冰淇淋的小姑娘呢？可不能把她落下了......", "name": "冰品店店主"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g8_siestavolcanomuseum_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "nam