..", "name": "緊張的路人"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "市政廳是這麼說的......", "name": "緊張的路人"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......你有沒有感覺到地面在震動？", "name": "不安的路人"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_994_1#6$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_994_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃尼斯！你有見到麗芙嗎！", "name": "哈莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_994_1#6$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不是留在家裡......", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#17$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_994_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛回來的時候發現她不見了，她沒有去找你嗎？", "name": "哈莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_994_1#6$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4106_bryota_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糟了......", "name": "埃尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4106_bryota_1#12$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "scrw", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g6_siestaunbuiltland_n", "screena